AD_MODULE.NAME: Docker Help Utils
AD_MODULE.DESCRIPTION: This module provides the infrastructure to distribute and manage Docker containers within the Etendo Classic environment, using a standardized method and Gradle tasks
AD_MODULE.HELP: This module provides the necessary infrastructure to distribute and run Docker containers in a modular way within the Etendo Classic environment. It offers a standardized method to package the infrastructure into modules and provides Gradle tasks to efficiently manage these containers.
